c: 11
v: 57
t: "Bwe munaava ku ekyo mazima nze mmaze okubatuusaako ekyo kye nnatumwa nakyo era Mukama omulabirizi wange mu kifo kya mmwe ajja kussaawo abantu abalala abatali mmwe, era temulina kabi kemugenda kumutuusaako. Mazima Mukama omulabirizi wange buli kyonna ekikolebwa akilondoola (tewali kimubuuka)"